@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.exp((tmp + (v1 + 0.70 + tmp + 0.61)))
    v0 = (0.47 / v0)
    v1 = tmp
    v1 = (wp.abs(wp.exp(v2 + 0.90)) / (wp.cos(tmp + 0.32) + (v2 + 0.51 - tmp + 0.75)))
    v1 = 0.04
    v0 = wp.exp(0.30)
    v1 = wp.abs(wp.cos((v1 + 0.59 / v0 + 0.35)))
    data[tid] = v0
